Name – Comments board/section
Brief Description – Users will have access to view the comments that were left by other users as well as post new comments 
Actors – Admin and Users will be able to view the full website 
Preconditions – No preconditions involved with the comments board
Basic Flow – The admin will be able to delete comments (if inappropriate, etc.), Users will be able to post new comments as well as see the old comments
Alternate Flows – No alternative flows for the comments board 
Post Conditions – New comments post to the website, but may be taken down if the admin feels that they’re inappropriate or irrelevant 

